DAT
id=qid::label=str::text=lstr::
5615::$$$message_0052_0000_0000$$$::There's a slithering sound.[lr]::
5616::$$$message_0052_0000_0001$$$::It's hard to determine whether the sound is a cry, something being dragged, or something festering.[lr]::
5617::$$$message_0052_0000_0002$$$::The sound represented everything.[lr]::
5618::$$$message_0052_0000_0003$$$::Here, there are only rotting things.[lr]::
5619::$$$message_0052_0000_0004$$$::The stone walls are as brittle as a decaying tree.[lr]::
5620::$$$message_0052_0000_0005$$$::The air smells sweet like honey.[lr]::
5621::$$$message_0052_0000_0006$$$::The creatures crawling on the ground are decomposing like ripe fruit, and even the time that passes in this space is rotten, meaningless.::
5622::$$$message_0052_0001_0000$$$::Everything here is worn out.[lr]::
5623::$$$message_0052_0001_0001$$$::The darkness is a graveyard for things that were never mourned on earth, the end of vindictive bloodlines.::
5624::$$$message_0052_0002_0000$$$::"It appears all seven have been selected."::
5625::$$$message_0052_0003_0000$$$::The largest gangrenous mass wriggles at the center of darkness. [lr]::
5626::$$$message_0052_0003_0001$$$::The sound of insects taints the air, along with a rancid, unpleasant stench.[lr]::
5627::$$$message_0052_0003_0002$$$::The master of this basement is rotten and decayed, yet alive, and [font italic=true]it[font italic=false] is surrounded by otherworldly worms.[lr]::
5628::$$$message_0052_0003_0003$$$::The insects that crawl up from the feet suck on [font italic=true]its[font italic=false] ankles, and once their suckers reach their host's flesh and bone, they continue to slowly burrow in to reach nerves.::
5629::$$$message_0052_0004_0000$$$::There are hundreds...nay, more than two hundred wriggling bugs.[lr]::
5630::$$$message_0052_0004_0001$$$::Any creature unlucky enough to be thrown onto this writhing carpet would die in moments.[lr]::
5631::$$$message_0052_0004_0002$$$::The insects would burrow in and devour its insides, leaving its flesh and bones intact, but taking it over.::
5632::$$$message_0052_0005_0000$$$::"It's not enough. These bugs will need to be replaced soon."::
5633::$$$message_0052_0006_0000$$$::Yet, [font italic=true]its[font italic=false] body does not break down.[lr]::
5634::$$$message_0052_0006_0001$$$::Rather, whenever the insects invade [font italic=true]its[font italic=false] body through the ankle, [font italic=true]its[font italic=false] body takes one step closer to completion.[lr]::
5635::$$$message_0052_0006_0002$$$::It is not being devoured by the insects.[lr]::
5636::$$$message_0052_0006_0003$$$::The massive insects that live in the basement are the ones being consumed, existing solely to be eaten by [font italic=true]it[font italic=false].[lr]::
5637::$$$message_0052_0006_0004$$$::There should be enough here to last a hundred years.[lr]::
5638::$$$message_0052_0006_0005$$$::That guarantees [font italic=true]it[font italic=false] at least that much time as [font italic=false]it[font italic=false] consumes these insects to live.::
5639::$$$message_0052_0007_0000$$$::"Not enough time. This battle may not be the final one. I must observe in silence if the conditions are not optimal this time."::
5640::$$$message_0052_0008_0000$$$::[font italic=true]It[font italic=false] twists its mouth in disapproval.[lr]::
5641::$$$message_0052_0008_0001$$$::The situation is in no way optimal.[lr]::
5642::$$$message_0052_0008_0002$$$::The battle is about to start once again, less than ten years after the last.[lr]::
5643::$$$message_0052_0008_0003$$$::The priest who is tasked with overseeing this ritual possesses two Servants, and the Servant rooted in Ryudou Temple has in turn summoned their own Servant.[lr]::
5644::$$$message_0052_0008_0004$$$::These conditions are not promising.[lr]::
5645::$$$message_0052_0008_0005$$$::A complete Grail simply will not be forged from such an unstable battle.[lr]::
5646::$$$message_0052_0008_0006$$$::The gates may open, but its contents will not be reachable.::
5647::$$$message_0052_0009_0000$$$::"Then I shall confine myself to simply observing this one. Unfortunately, my pawns are at the optimal state right now."::
5648::$$$message_0052_0010_0000$$$::The conditions to fight over the Holy Grail are abysmal.[lr]::
5649::$$$message_0052_0010_0001$$$::However, the [font italic=true]thing[font italic=false] that was painstakingly created is in its ideal form.[lr]::
5650::$$$message_0052_0010_0002$$$::If released, it would surely reach it.[lr]::
5651::$$$message_0052_0010_0003$$$::As long as the proper steps are taken, the Holy Grail should be attainable.[lr]::
5652::$$$message_0052_0010_0004$$$::After all, contents of the Holy Grail have been implanted inside them.[lr]::
5653::$$$message_0052_0010_0005$$$::For ten years, fragments of the Holy Grail have spread into and throughout their nerves.[lr]::
5654::$$$message_0052_0010_0006$$$::It is only natural for things originating from the same source be attracted to one another.::
5655::$$$message_0052_0011_0000$$$::"Hmph. There may be a next time for me, but that thing isn't likely to last long. I may have I received it as a placental vessel initially, but I never expected it to be as good as it turned out."::
5656::$$$message_0052_0012_0000$$$::The thing was an experiment, but now it has perfectly adapted to its purpose.[lr]::
5657::$$$message_0052_0012_0001$$$::It was supposed to be disposed of, but it ought to be used if it proves useful.[lr]::
5658::$$$message_0052_0012_0002$$$::In either case, the plan is to dispose of it anyway.[lr]::
5659::$$$message_0052_0012_0003$$$::The thing is bound to be discarded, whether it loses in battle, is destroyed, or disabled.::
5660::$$$message_0052_0013_0000$$$::"Which raises one issue: [lr]::
5661::$$$message_0052_0013_0001$$$::How will I motivate it to do its job?" ::
5662::$$$message_0052_0014_0000$$$::For some reason, the [font italic=true]compatible masterpiece[font italic=false] refuses to fight.[lr]::
5663::$$$message_0052_0014_0001$$$::One approach would be taking over its mind, but it has put up a solid mental defense.[lr]::
5664::$$$message_0052_0014_0002$$$::Well, that is why I wanted a vessel that possesses strong Magic Circuits.[lr]::
5665::$$$message_0052_0014_0003$$$::It is only logical for something talented to be hardy in the face of poison trying to invade it.[lr]::
5666::$$$message_0052_0014_0004$$$::Then, shall the obedient doll or the outstanding pupil be chosen?[lr]::
5667::$$$message_0052_0014_0005$$$::If the latter, brainwashing would be out of the question.::
5668::$$$message_0052_0015_0000$$$::"Just once...as long as there is a small opening, it will surely seek the Holy Grail on its own. But what to do..."::
5669::$$$message_0052_0016_0000$$$::Creating that small opening is the difficult part.[lr]::
5670::$$$message_0052_0016_0001$$$::That thing is not so weak as to be broken by coercion.[lr]::
5671::$$$message_0052_0016_0002$$$::If it could break easily, it would have broken eleven years ago.[lr]::
5672::$$$message_0052_0016_0003$$$::It has erected quite the fortress to defend itself, but it simply has no blade with which to fight back.[lr]::
5673::$$$message_0052_0016_0004$$$::If it is to break, it must be from within.[lr]::
5674::$$$message_0052_0016_0005$$$::Its futile emotions should be the key to transforming it.::
5675::$$$message_0052_0017_0000$$$::"So you've come. Then it is time to create an opening."::
5676::$$$message_0052_0018_0000$$$::Descending footsteps echo in the darkness.[lr]::
5677::$$$message_0052_0018_0001$$$::The person walks in towards the center of the decaying insects.::
5678::$$$message_0052_0018_0002$$$::The thing asks a predictable question: ::
5679::$$$message_0052_0018_0003$$$::[font italic=true]Do all Masters have to be killed?[font italic=false]::
5680::$$$message_0052_0019_0000$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false]::
5681::$$$message_0052_0020_0000$$$::Of course, there is no need to answer.[lr]::
5682::$$$message_0052_0020_0001$$$::All Masters must die.[lr]::
5683::$$$message_0052_0020_0002$$$::All Servants must be seized.[lr]::
5684::$$$message_0052_0020_0003$$$::That is the ethos writhing within this basement.[lr]::
5685::$$$message_0052_0020_0004$$$::But that thought is pushed aside.::
5686::$$$message_0052_0021_0000$$$::"If that is how you feel, then I have no choice. We shall resolve ourselves to simply observe once again."::
5687::$$$message_0052_0022_0000$$$::[font italic=true]It[font italic=false] utters.[lr]::
5688::$$$message_0052_0022_0001$$$::It emits a sigh of relief, and the mood softens.[lr]::
5689::$$$message_0052_0022_0002$$$::After the thing indicates that it has no intention to fight by gently smiling...::
5690::$$$message_0052_0023_0000$$$::"But that will lead to a rather unfortunate outcome. Of all the vessels created this time, the Tohsaka girl has turned out to be quite formidable. If there is to be a winner, it will likely be her."::
5691::$$$message_0052_0024_0000$$$::[font italic=true]It[font italic=false] murmurs in a disappointed tone.[lr]::
5692::$$$message_0052_0024_0001$$$::"..."::
5693::$$$message_0052_0024_0002$$$::The air feels slack once again.[lr]::
5694::$$$message_0052_0024_0003$$$::Faint disappointment flickers like an ember in the basement.[lr]::
5695::$$$message_0052_0024_0004$$$::The thing that has resisted fighting this entire time suddenly shows signs of reconsidering after hearing [font italic=true]its[font italic=false] single statement.[lr]::
5696::$$$message_0052_0024_0005$$$::The thing is wavering.[lr]::
5697::$$$message_0052_0024_0006$$$::A slight crack.[lr]::
5698::$$$message_0052_0024_0007$$$::The thing does not even notice, but now a slight, unintended opening cracks their defenses.::
5699::$$$message_0052_0025_0000$$$::"...Heh."::
5700::$$$message_0052_0026_0000$$$::[font italic=true]It[font italic=false] laughs.[lr]::
5701::$$$message_0052_0026_0001$$$::Swarmed by worms and still rotting, [font italic=true]it[font italic=false] still maintains its human shape as it laughs.::

